### Get All Tags
GET {{host}}:{{port}}/api/tags?search=tag

### Create Tags
POST {{host}}:{{port}}/api/tags
Content-Type: application/json

[
  "new tag"
]

### Get Media for tag
GET {{host}}:{{port}}/api/tags/fbcbb87b-0791-4c35-a654-078f7be0f1c8/media

### Delete tag
DELETE {{host}}:{{port}}/api/tags/af2e1aa3-93d9-4b94-8a29-2c5dfd600d33
